<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8 font-weight: 500">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GeoStruct Pro - 15 Essential Geotechnical Formulas & Computational Solver</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;900&family=Orbitron:wght@400;600;700;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; 
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s, border-color 0.3s; 
        }
        
        h1, h2, h3, h4, p, span, label, button, input, div, i {
            transition: color 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .cyber-font { font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; }
        .mono-font { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
        .formula-card { transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); cursor: help; }
        .formula-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
        
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; height: 6px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--scrollbar-track); }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--scrollbar-thumb); border-radius: 3px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #f59e0b; }

        /* THEME CONFIGURATION DYNAMIC MAPPING */
        .theme-dark {
            --bg-main: #0f172a;
            --bg-card: #1e293b;
            --bg-header: #020617;
            --border-color: #334155;
            --text-main: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #cbd5e1;
            --bg-input: #020617;
            --scrollbar-track: #0f172a;
            --scrollbar-thumb: #334155;
            --neon-amber: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.25);
            --neon-emerald: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.25);
            --bg-tooltip: #020617;
        }
        
        .theme-light {
            --bg-main: #f1f5f9;
            --bg-card: #ffffff;
            --bg-header: #e2e8f0;
            --border-color: #94a3b8;
            --text-main: #020617; 
            --text-muted: #334155; 
            --bg-input: #f8fafc;
            --scrollbar-track: #e2e8f0;
            --scrollbar-thumb: #cbd5e1;
            --neon-amber: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15);
            --neon-emerald: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15);
            --bg-tooltip: #ffffff;
        }

        .neon-border-amber {
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--neon-amber);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        .neon-border-emerald {
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--neon-emerald);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        .glow-text-amber { text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4); }
        .drag-handle { cursor: move; user-select: none; }

        .geo-custom-tooltip {
            position: fixed;
            pointer-events: none;
            background: var(--bg-tooltip);
            border: 2px solid #f59e0b;
            color: var(--text-main);
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            max-width: 320px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            z-index: 1000;
            display: none;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .formula-desc {
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        @keyframes pulse-glow {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.7); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(245, 158, 11, 1); }
        }
        .chat-trigger-btn {
            animation: pulse-glow 2s infinite;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="theme-dark bg-[var(--bg-main)] text-[var(--text-main)] min-h-screen flex flex-col selection:bg-amber-500 selection:text-black" id="appBody">

    <div class="h-1.5 w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 via-orange-500 to-yellow-400 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(245,158,11,0.6)]"></div>

    <div class="geo-custom-tooltip font-mono" id="geoLiveTooltip"></div>

    <header class="bg-[var(--bg-header)] border-b-2 border-[var(--border-color)] shadow-xl sticky top-0 z-50 backdrop-blur-md px-4 py-4">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="bg-amber-500 text-slate-950 p-2.5 rounded-bl-xl rounded-tr-xl font-black text-xl tracking-wider cyber-font shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(245,158,11,0.4)]">
                    GEO<span class="text-orange-600">S</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-xl font-black tracking-widest cyber-font text-[var(--text-main)]">
                        GEOSTRUCT <span class="text-amber-500">PRO</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-xs text-amber-500 font-mono font-bold tracking-wider">15 CORE GEOTECHNICAL SOLVER // COMPLIANCE STATION</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="relative w-full md:w-72">
                <span class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 flex items-center pl-3 pointer-events-none text-slate-400">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass text-xs"></i>
                </span>
                <input class="w-full pl-9 pr-4 py-2 bg-[var(--bg-input)] border-2 border-[var(--border-color)] rounded-lg text-[var(--text-main)] placeholder-slate-400 focus:outline-none focus:border-amber-500 text-xs font-mono font-bold" id="searchInput" onkeyup="filterDatabase()" placeholder="Cari rumus atau parameter..." type="text" />
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 w-full md:w-auto justify-end">
                <button class="bg-[var(--bg-input)] border-2 border-[var(--border-color)] text-xs font-mono font-black px-3 py-2 rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition-all shadow-md flex items-center gap-1.5 text-amber-500 hover:border-amber-500" onclick="toggleThemeInterface()" type="button">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-moon" id="themeIcon"></i> <span id="themeText">DARK MODE</span>
                </button>

                <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-teal-600 text-white text-xs font-mono font-black px-4 py-2 rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition-all shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 hover:from-emerald-500 hover:to-teal-500" onclick="openHelpModal()" type="button">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i> <span>HELP &amp; CREATOR</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="flex-1 max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-4 py-8 flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6">
        
        <aside class="w-full lg:w-72 shrink-0">
            <div class="bg-[var(--bg-card)] p-4 rounded-xl border-2 border-[var(--border-color)] sticky top-24 space-y-4 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-xl">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-xs font-black text-amber-500 font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 px-2">Kategori Modul Geoteknik</h2>
                    <nav class="space-y-1.5" id="categoryNav">
                        <button class="cat-btn w-full text-left px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-bold bg-amber-500 text-slate-950 flex items-center justify-between transition-colors cursor-pointer" id="cat-all-btn" onclick="filterCategory('all')">
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group mr-2 w-3.5"></i>Semua Rumus Inti</span>
                            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-950/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-black" id="count-all">15</span>
                        </button>
                        <button class="cat-btn w-full text-left px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-bold text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-between transition-colors cursor-pointer" onclick="filterCategory('stress-strength')">
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt mr-2 w-3.5"></i>Stress &amp; Strength</span>
                            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-400/20 text-[var(--text-main)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-black" id="count-stress-strength">0</span>
                        </button>
                        <button class="cat-btn w-full text-left px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-bold text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-between transition-colors cursor-pointer" onclick="filterCategory('flow-seepage')">
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-water mr-2 w-3.5"></i>Flow &amp; Seepage</span>
                            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-400/20 text-[var(--text-main)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-black" id="count-flow-seepage">0</span>
                        </button>
                        <button class="cat-btn w-full text-left px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-bold text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-between transition-colors cursor-pointer" onclick="filterCategory('settlement-consolidation')">
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-down-long mr-2 w-3.5"></i>Settlement &amp; Consolidation</span>
                            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-400/20 text-[var(--text-main)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-black" id="count-settlement-consolidation">0</span>
                        </button>
                        <button class="cat-btn w-full text-left px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-bold text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-between transition-colors cursor-pointer" onclick="filterCategory('earth-pressure')">
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved mr-2 w-3.5"></i>Earth Pressure</span>
                            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-400/20 text-[var(--text-main)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-black" id="count-earth-pressure">0</span>
                        </button>
                        <button class="cat-btn w-full text-left px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono font-bold text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-between transition-colors cursor-pointer" onclick="filterCategory('stability-stress')">
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line mr-2 w-3.5"></i>Stability &amp; Distribution</span>
                            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-400/20 text-[var(--text-main)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-black" id="count-stability-stress">0</span>
                        </button>
                    </nav>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-[var(--bg-input)] p-3 rounded-lg border-2 border-[var(--border-color)] text-xs font-mono text-[var(--text-muted)] space-y-2 leading-relaxed font-bold">
                    <span class="font-black text-amber-500 block mb-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation mr-1"></i>Key Reminders:</span>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-amber-500 mt-0.5 font-bold"></i><span>Selalu periksa nilai tegangan efektif sigma' dahulu.</span></div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-amber-500 mt-0.5 font-bold"></i><span>Jangan abaikan tekanan air pori u.</span></div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-amber-500 mt-0.5 font-bold"></i><span>Target SF ≥ 1.5 untuk stabilitas lereng aman.</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <section class="flex-1 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center bg-[var(--bg-card)] px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-[var(--border-color)] gap-2 shadow-md">
                <span class="text-xs font-black font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--text-muted)]" id="currentCategoryTitle">Menampilkan Semua Formula</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-amber-500 font-mono font-black glow-text-amber" id="itemCounter">0 Item Terdaftar</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4" id="formulaContainer"></div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <div class="fixed bottom-6 right-6 z-[60] font-mono flex flex-col items-end" id="floatingChatContainer">
        <div class="hidden w-80 h-96 bg-slate-900 border-2 border-slate-700 rounded-xl shadow-2xl flex flex-col mb-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 neon-border-amber" id="chatWindow">
            <div class="bg-slate-950 px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-800 flex justify-between items-center">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></div>
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-amber-400 uppercase tracking-wider"><i class="fa-solid fa-robot mr-1"></i> GeoBot Assistant</span>
                </div>
                <button class="text-slate-400 hover:text-rose-400 cursor-pointer p-1" onclick="toggleFloatingChat()">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-sm"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex-1 p-3 overflow-y-auto space-y-2.5 text-[11px] bg-slate-950/40 text-slate-200" id="chatMessages">
                <div class="bg-slate-800 text-slate-100 p-2.5 rounded-lg max-w-[85%] self-start border border-slate-700 font-medium">
                    Halo! Saya <strong>GeoBot</strong>. Ada yang bisa saya bantu terkait kriteria formula geoteknik, parameter <strong>Kritis</strong>, atau penanganan kondisi <strong>Tidak Aman</strong>?
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="px-2 py-1.5 bg-slate-950/90 border-t border-slate-800 flex gap-1 overflow-x-auto whitespace-nowrap text-[9px]">
                <button class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-amber-500 hover:text-slate-950 text-slate-100 font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded border border-slate-600 cursor-pointer" onclick="sendQuickQuestion('Berapa limit kritis untuk FOS Lereng?')">FOS Lereng</button>
                <button class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-amber-500 hover:text-slate-950 text-slate-100 font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded border border-slate-600 cursor-pointer" onclick="sendQuickQuestion('Apa itu bahaya sand boiling?')">Sand Boiling</button>
                <button class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-amber-500 hover:text-slate-950 text-slate-100 font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded border border-slate-600 cursor-pointer" onclick="sendQuickQuestion('Berapa batas penurunan lempung?')">Batas Sc</button>
            </div>

            <form class="p-2 bg-slate-950 border-t border-slate-800 flex gap-1.5" onsubmit="handleChatSubmit(event)">
                <input autocomplete="off" class="flex-1 px-3 py-1.5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg text-slate-100 text-xs focus:outline-none focus:border-amber-500 font-medium" id="chatInput" placeholder="Tanya sesuatu..." type="text" />
                <button class="bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-400 text-slate-950 p-2 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center aspect-square w-8 cursor-pointer" type="submit">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane text-xs"></i>
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <button class="chat-trigger-btn bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-400 text-slate-950 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl cursor-pointer transition-transform hover:scale-110" onclick="toggleFloatingChat()">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-comments text-lg" id="chatTriggerIcon"></i>
        </button>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-slate-950 border-t-2 border-slate-900 py-6 px-6 mt-auto text-slate-400">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-xs font-mono flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
            <p>© 2026 GeoStruct Pro Workspace // Core Solver Engine Stable.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-[11px]">
                <span>Platform Framework Powered by</span>
                <span class="text-amber-500 font-black"><i class="fa-solid fa-leaf text-emerald-500"></i> Mohamad Hartadi</span>
            </div>
            <p class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px]"><i class="fa-solid fa-microchip text-amber-500"></i> PLAXIS, GEO5, GeoStudio (SLOPE/W, SEEP/W) Verification.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <div class="hidden fixed inset-0 z-50 bg-black/70 backdrop-blur-sm flex items-center justify-center p-4" id="calcModal">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border-2 border-slate-700 rounded-xl max-w-2xl w-full overflow-hidden shadow-2xl flex flex-col transition-all neon-border-amber text-slate-100">
            <div class="bg-slate-950 px-6 py-4 border-b border-slate-800 flex justify-between items-center">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-amber-400 font-bold font-mono text-xs">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-square-root-variable text-sm"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-white font-black" id="modalTitle">Interactive Engineering Solver</h3>
                </div>
                <button class="text-slate-400 hover:text-rose-400 text-lg cursor-pointer p-1" onclick="closeCalculator()">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="p-6 overflow-y-auto max-h-[80vh] space-y-4">
                <div class="bg-slate-950 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-800 font-mono flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-3">
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider block mb-1">Persamaan Inti:</span>
                        <code class="text-sm text-amber-400 font-black block overflow-x-auto py-1 glow-text-amber" id="modalMathExpression"></code>
                    </div>
                    <button type="button" onclick="askGeoBotAboutCurrentFormula()" class="shrink-0 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white text-[11px] font-black px-3 py-2 rounded shadow-md flex items-center gap-1.5 transition-all">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-robot"></i> Tanya GeoBot Rumus Ini
                    </button>
                </div>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 pt-2 font-mono text-xs" id="dynamicInputs"></div>
                
                <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-800">
                    <button class="w-full bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-400 text-slate-950 font-mono font-black tracking-wider py-3 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-2 cursor-pointer shadow-md uppercase text-xs transition-all" onclick="calculateResult()">
                        Kalkulasi Nilai Output <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt text-xs text-orange-700"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
                
                <div class="hidden space-y-3" id="resultBox">
                    <div class="bg-slate-950 p-4 rounded-lg border shadow-inner" id="resultBorderBox">
                        <span class="text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-wider block mb-1" id="resultTitleLabel"><i class="fa-solid fa-square-poll-vertical mr-1"></i>Hasil Komputasi Eksak:</span>
                        <div class="text-xl font-mono font-black" id="calcOutput"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-slate-950/80 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-800 text-xs font-mono space-y-2">
                        <div class="text-amber-500 font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-slate-800 pb-1">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-brain mr-1"></i> Engineering Interpretative Log &amp; Evaluation
                        </div>
                        <div class="space-y-2 text-slate-200 text-[11px] leading-relaxed font-medium">
                            <p id="logInputMeaning"></p>
                            <p id="logKeyPoints"></p>
                            <div class="p-2 rounded border mt-1" id="logAdviceConclusion"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="fixed inset-0 z-[60] hidden bg-black/50 flex items-center justify-center p-4 shadow-2xl" id="helpModal">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl w-full max-w-2xl max-h-[90vh] flex flex-col shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300 neon-border-emerald text-slate-100 select-none" id="draggableHelpPanel">
            
            <div class="drag-handle p-4 bg-slate-950 rounded-t-xl border-b border-slate-800 flex justify-between items-center relative" id="helpDragHandle">
                <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 px-3 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-slate-950 text-[9px] font-mono text-emerald-400 tracking-widest border border-emerald-500/30">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrows-up-down-left-right mr-1"></i> DRAG TERMINAL PANEL
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-emerald-400 font-bold font-mono text-xs tracking-wider uppercase">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-terminal"></i> CENTRAL SYSTEM DOCUMENTATION &amp; HELP
                </div>
                <button class="text-slate-400 hover:text-rose-400 cursor-pointer p-1" onclick="closeHelpModal()">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-xmark text-lg"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="p-5 overflow-y-auto space-y-5 font-mono text-xs text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                
                <div class="border border-slate-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
                    <div class="bg-amber-500 text-slate-950 px-3 py-2 flex items-center gap-2 font-black text-xs">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i> 1. BATASAN TEKNIS PARMETER KRITIS &amp; BAHAYA
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 bg-slate-950/80 space-y-4 text-slate-100">
                        <div class="border-b border-slate-800 pb-3">
                            <span class="text-amber-400 font-black block text-sm mb-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line mr-1.5"></i>FOS Lereng (Factor of Safety)</span>
                            <ul class="list-none pl-1 space-y-1 text-xs font-medium text-slate-300">
                                <li>• <span class="text-emerald-400 font-bold">Aman</span>: FOS ≥ 1.5 (Sesuai dengan regulasi jangka panjang nasional)</li>
                                <li>• <span class="text-orange-400 font-bold">Kritis</span>: 1.0 ≤ FOS &lt; 1.5 (Rentan terjadi kelongsoran jika dipicu hujan atau gempa)</li>
                                <li>• <span class="text-red-500 font-bold">Bahaya / Gagal</span>: FOS &lt; 1.0 (Lereng runtuh secara mekanis)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="border-b border-slate-800 pb-3">
                            <span class="text-teal-400 font-black block text-sm mb-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-water mr-1.5"></i>Sand Boiling &amp; Piping (Gradien Hidrolik i)</span>
                            <ul class="list-none pl-1 space-y-1 text-xs font-medium text-slate-300">
                                <li>• <span class="text-emerald-400 font-bold">Aman</span>: i &lt; 0.75 (Aliran rembesan air tanah laminar stabil)</li>
                                <li>• <span class="text-orange-400 font-bold">Kritis</span>: i ≥ 0.75 (Laju aliran cepat mendekati batas didih pasir murni)</li>
                                <li>• <span class="text-red-500 font-bold">Bahaya / Tidak Aman</span>: i ≥ 1.0 (Terjadi kegagalan erosi internal piping atau sand boiling destruktif)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <span class="text-purple-400 font-black block text-sm mb-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-down-long mr-1.5"></i>Batas Sc Penurunan (Consolidation Settlement)</span>
                            <ul class="list-none pl-1 space-y-1 text-xs font-medium text-slate-300">
                                <li>• <span class="text-emerald-400 font-bold">Aman</span>: Sc ≤ 50 mm (Deformasi elastis struktur masih mampu bertoleransi)</li>
                                <li>• <span class="text-red-500 font-bold">Kritis / Bahaya</span>: Sc &gt; 50 mm (Penurunan konsolidasi lempung masif, memicu retak struktural gedung)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
